MemoServ Operator Commands:
 
These commands are available to Services Operators:
 
OSEND      Sends a global memo to all SOPs/SAs/SRAs/CODERs
 
These commands are available to Services Administrators:
 
LIMIT      Sets the maximum number of memos a user is allowed to have
 
These commands are available to Services Roots:
 
GLOBAL     Sends a memo to ALL registered nicks
INFO       Shows the given user's memos status
 
*** End of OHelp ***